{
  "stem": "16395.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they took us, and they took us to Tschenstochau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- I think it was in '44, the beginning of '44, because-- maybe March of '44.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know any of those dates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember I came to Tschenstochau and again, I worked by the same machine, but we had a terrible meister.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He gave us-- he gave us the work to work double what we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we learned in the day while we could, we did a little bit more and would put it away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And we were all young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Tschenstochau-- in Skarzysko I was doing-- I was knitting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I made a sweater for meister-- for one, not the German, for the Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he used to give me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He used to give me on Wednesdays soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He brought the wool.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought the wool and I made it and I-- and I gave him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I finished the sweater.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was up all night, and I finished the sweater.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he wanted some gloves, so he brought me the knitting-- knitting-- two knittings and he bought me five knittings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Already I didn't give them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he brought me wool.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the same night, they took us away to Tschenstochau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I came to Tschenstochau, I had five knitting things, and I had a lot of wool.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I figured, I'll start making a sweater or whatever is for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was sitting in there after work, I was sitting and knitting outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Came a-- a boy to me-- and this is my husband-- and he said to me, would you knit for me a sweater?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have two old sweaters, and I would like to make one.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
